clueServer
Class Pieces

java.lang.Object
  clueServer.Pieces

public class Pieces
extends Object

Class semantics and roles:
Pieces keeps track of player locations throughout the game. It also sets the initial starting points of all the players.

Information maintenance:
Creation: Pieces is created at start up by GameBoard.
Deletion: Pieces is deleted when the game has finished or otherwise been terminated.

Author:
Matt SeGall (Class Skeletons & Code)
